description:
Honored to be changing the world with such fine individuals!  Thank you @drbuttar! “Defending Those Who Defend Us! This could quite possibly be the most important video series I’ve put out in the last few months!  Part 1 gets released at 9 pm New York time tonight.

This is critical information that everyone must know. And information that many of us didn’t even recognize.  And it all starts with our military, those who put their lives on the line to defend us. 

But how have we as a nation, rewarded them? How have we as a global society, rewarded all of our servicemen and women? This is part one of four. All four parts will be released in the next 48 hours. 

Watch this and share it with everyone you know. Pass it on and paid forward. This is especially important if you have a loved one that serves in the military right now. 

Click on the link in the profile to watch the full video.  Or click on the YouTube link.  And do not make the mistake of thinking that this is not important.”
